{"title":"资助","grey":true,"time":"2022 年 8 月 9 日","shareable":true,"id":"intro/subsidize/index","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"p","heading":"关于资助","text":["作为一所倡导“尊重的教育”理念的师范大学，学校一直十分重视家庭经济困难学生的资助工作，构建了以国家助学贷款为主体，勤工助学为主导，“奖、贷、助、补、减”五位一体的家庭经济困难学生资助工作体系，并成立了专门从事资助工作的机构——学生资助管理中心。所以即便您有经济困难，在收到大学录取通知书的时候，面对学费和生活费，也不必担心。"]},{"tag":"list","items":[{"text":"资助体系介绍","icon":"about","path":"intro/subsidize/intro"},{"text":"资助申请流程","icon":"subsidize-apply","path":"intro/subsidize/application"},{"text":"资助计划","desc":"金额与人数","icon":"money","path":"intro/subsidize/plan"},{"text":"资助工作机构","icon":"office","path":"intro/subsidize/agency"},{"text":"入学绿色通道","icon":"green-tunnel","path":"intro/subsidize/green-tunnel"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"助学贷款","items":[{"text":"国家助学贷款","icon":"about","path":"intro/subsidize/loan/intro"},{"text":"生源地信用助学贷款","icon":"home","path":"intro/subsidize/loan/hometown"},{"text":"生源地信用助学贷款","icon":"school","path":"intro/subsidize/loan/school"},{"text":"更多","icon":"more","path":"intro/subsidize/loan/index"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"通知公告","items":[{"text":"2021 - 2022 学年资助对象评定","icon":"notice","path":"intro/subsidize/notice"},{"text":"2021 至 2022 学年学校助学金评审通知","icon":"notice","path":"intro/subsidize/help-notice"}]}]}